title: Aladdin's
typeOfFood: Vegan-friendly, Lacto, Ovo, Juice bar, Take-out, Middle Eastern, Non-veg
description: Serves meat, veg options available. Part of chain. Menu is mostly meat but has some veg including juice bar, smoothies, salads, hummus wrap, falafel, baba ganouj, lentil soups. No fake meats or tofu. Desserts are not vegan. Dressings are made without sugar. Patio seating in summer.
